    <h2>Ohcanjoavkkut</h2>
    <p>Aiddostahtton ohcamis sáhtát geavahit eanet ohcanjoavkkuid ovtta ohcamii.</p>
    <p><strong>Lasit ohcanjoavku</strong> –boallu lasiha ođđa joavkku ohcangittiid.</p>
    <p><strong>Sihko ohcanjoavku</strong>–boallu sihkku ohcanjoavkku.</p> 
